data.description: Welcome home! Located in Lake Carolina this home features 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a FROG/bonus room that can easily be utilized as a media room, office, or guest space. Upon entry you will find a family/dining room featuring wainscoting, crown molding throughout, and a gas fireplace. With a fully finished garage and epoxy floors the possibilities are endless. Sip your favorite beverage on the cozy deck that perfect for guests and entertaining.   Less than a 10 minute drive from Lake Carolina’s very own Town Center, featuring locally owned restaurants, shoppes and seasonal events. Less than 15 minutes to shopping at the Village at Sandhills, 30 minutes to Fort Jackson and Downtown Columbia. Come see what this home has to offer you today! Call/Text for a virtual tour!  (Back on the market at no fault of the sellers)
